%%{init: {'theme':'default'}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> Locked: not phase 1<br/>+ prior phase incomplete
    [*] --> Ready: phase 1<br/>(fresh start)

    Locked --> Ready: prior phase fully complete<br/>(weeks + boss)
    Ready --> InProgress: any week ticked partially<br/>or fully complete
    InProgress --> BossUnlocked: all weeks<br/>in phase complete
    BossUnlocked --> Complete: boss defeated
    Complete --> [*]

    note right of BossUnlocked
        Boss card glows + becomes
        clickable. CSS animation
        on .boss-card.unlocked.
    end note
